Package: rnaseq.hs.lf.tgfb.mcti
Title: RNA-seq of Lactate Transporter Inhibition in Human Lung Myofibroblasts
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person(
        given = "William", 
        family = "Oldham", 
        email = "wm.oldham@gmail.com", 
        role = c("aut", "cre"),
        comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3029-4866")
    )
Description: This package is a data repository for RNA-seq data obtained to 
    study the impact of lactate transport inhibition on myofibroblast 
    differentiation. In the first experiment, normal human lung fibroblasts 
    (Lonza) were treated with TGFβ (2 ng/mL) in combination with MCT1 inhibitor 
    AZD3965 (100 nM) or MCT4 inhibitor VB124 (10 μM), separately or together, 
    with DMSO (0.1%) as the vehicle control. In the second experiment, normal 
    human lung fibroblasts were treated with MCT4 inhibitor VB253 (10 μM) or 
    DMSO (0.1%) as the vehicle control. RNA was obtained after 48 h of treatment 
    and submitted for sequencing at BGI Genomics.
